      <title>德国两年期国债收益率自 2022 年以来首次跌破 2%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/german-two-year-yield-drops-below-2-for-first-time-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受地缘政治担忧影响，投资者纷纷购买避险资产，德国债券价格大幅上涨，短期收益率近两年来首次跌破 2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/german-two-year-yield-drops-below-2-for-first-time-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:41:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国东部和墨西哥湾港口历史性罢工开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/historic-strike-at-eastern-us-and-gulf-ports-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于未能就新合同达成一致，美国东海岸和墨西哥湾沿岸各大港口的码头工人近 50 年来首次罢工。摩根大通称，罢工可能使美国经济每天损失高达 45 亿美元。工会要求提高工资和就业保障。彭博社的 Dani Burger 正在新泽西州伊丽莎白市的一个主要港口工作。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/historic-strike-at-eastern-us-and-gulf-ports-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:40:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pimco 的 Browne 预计第三季度经济将走出低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/pimco-s-browne-expects-a-bounceback-from-third-quarter-lull</link>
      <description><![CDATA[太平洋投资管理公司 (Pimco) 多元资产策略投资组合经理 Erin Browne 表示，美国大选前“各公司都在观望，等待更多明朗因素”，但她并不认为当前的环境意味着经济放缓。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/pimco-s-browne-expects-a-bounceback-from-third-quarter-lull</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:39:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Unieuro 创始人反对 Fnac 收购，称其估值过低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/unieuro-founders-oppose-fnac-bid-citing-steep-undervaluation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Unieuro SpA 的创始人反对 Fnac Darty SA 的收购要约，理由是该收购要约严重低估了这家意大利电子产品零售商的价值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/unieuro-founders-oppose-fnac-bid-citing-steep-undervaluation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:33:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>二叠纪天然气开始通过德克萨斯州马特洪管道输送</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/permian-gas-starts-flowing-via-matterhorn-pipeline-in-texas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马特洪峰快线管道 (Matterhorn Express Pipeline) 已开始向 Williams Cos. 的 Transco 管道输送天然气，这是二叠纪盆地中游基础设施期待已久的补充。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/permian-gas-starts-flowing-via-matterhorn-pipeline-in-texas</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:31:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特矿业部长认为在加拿大进行交易没有障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/saudi-s-mining-minister-sees-no-obstacles-to-dealmaking-in-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管沙特阿拉伯政府规定限制国有外国实体的投资，但沙特阿拉伯矿业部长并不认为有任何障碍阻止该国与加拿大采矿业进行交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/saudi-s-mining-minister-sees-no-obstacles-to-dealmaking-in-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:29:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度批准采取措施遏制股票衍生品交易热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/india-clears-steps-to-curb-trading-rush-in-stock-derivatives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于散户参与度不断提高，投机性赌注达到全球最高水平，印度证券监管机构周二宣布采取措施限制该国股票衍生品交易的激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/india-clears-steps-to-curb-trading-rush-in-stock-derivatives</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 12:59:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>裕信银行称欧盟需要更大的银行，首席执行官瞄准德国商业银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/unicredit-ceo-says-eu-needs-bigger-banks-as-he-eyes-commerzbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行（UniCredit SpA）首席执行官安德里亚·奥塞尔（Andrea Orcel）正在寻求收购德国竞争对手德国商业银行（Commerzbank AG）。他表示，欧洲的银行规模不足以满足欧盟的融资需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/unicredit-ceo-says-eu-needs-bigger-banks-as-he-eyes-commerzbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 12:45:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
